Airraptor was on patrole when he suddenly spotted a small battle going on, 
down on the ground. One of the bots was his team mate Dinotron. He thought 
about going down to help him, but one of the bots he was confronting looked 
pretty big and powerful. So he stayed up high in the air to keep spying on 
them.
